# Data Questions and Stories


#### In lessons 5 and 6, students explore the art of crafting effective data-driven questions and learn how to tell compelling data stories, focusing on the clarity, relevance, and ethical implications of their inquiries while examining real-life examples to understand the elements of impactful data storytelling.

---

